ments that would be beneficial. And list any preferred hard and soft skills. Example Assistant Accountant requirements Bachelor's degree required Concentration in accounting preferred Associate's degree with 5+ years' experience will be considered Prior experience working with a Certified Public Accountant 2+ years' experience for applicants with Bachelor's degrees Proficiency in Quickbooks Assistant Accountant related job titles: Accounting Assistant Junior Accountant Office Accounting Assistant Accountant (Part-Time) Accounting Associate Ready to find your next hire? Post a Job Â© 2020 SH Inc. |Â PrivacyÂ |Â TermsÂ |Â Privacy CenterÂ  |Â Do Not Sell My Personal Information"
